<H3> <TI>   Columnist Views Banknotes Issued in Hong Kong </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Columnist Views Banknotes Issued in Hong Kong </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK0605025894 Beijing RENMIN RIBAO OVERSEAS EDITION in 
Chinese 5 May 94 p 5 </F>

<F P=103> HK0605025894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing RENMIN RIBAO OVERSEAS EDITION </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


