<H3> <TI>   BOC Hong Kong Group Names New Director </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    BOC Hong Kong Group Names New Director </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK0605031694 Hong Kong TA KUNG PAO in Chinese 5 May 94 p 2 </F>
