Central Committee of the Vietnamese Communist Party, thanked Wei 
for the warm reception here. 
  He voiced the hope that his delegation's visit will help to 
further the exchanges and friendship between the discipline 
inspection departments of the two parties. 
  After the meeting, Wei hosted a banquet for the visitors. 
  The Vietnamese visitors arrived here yesterday for an 11-day 
visit to China at the invitation of the CPC Central Commission 
for Discipline Inspection. 

