<H3> <TI>   National Petroleum Corporation Expands Overseas Operations </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    National Petroleum Corporation Expands Overseas Operations </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK0805072594 Beijing CHINA DAILY (BUSINESS WEEKLY) in 
English 8-14 May 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> HK0805072594 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing CHINA DAILY (BUSINESS WEEKLY) </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
